726725f-b.text:
(old No.) 684 Fresh Pond Road (tracks thereon), at the S.W. corner of Gates Ave., showing the G. Hulst farmhouse in a set of four views. The owners were G. Hulst 1852-1860, and E.T. Hulst 1873-1896. It was demolished in
March 1925.
March 1923.
Views 1 3 3.
Views 2 & 41 1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
